title: Green Elephant Vegetarian Bistro
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Thai, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Asian, Pan Asian
description: Pan Asian cuisine restaurant established 2007. Offers a concise lunch menu and a more expanded dinner menu. Sample items such as crispy wonton, spicy green leaves salad, tofu and vegetable teriyaki, watercress veggie-duck. Uses vegetarian soy meats. Opened another location in Portsmouth in 2015.
